metadata.description:
Hola! I’m Amy Correa Bell, a So Cal native based in the San Fernando Valley. I got into the web3 space exactly one year ago and Wowww! I’m so freakin grateful to be releasing my 3rd NFT here on Sound.xyz and excited to share a sneak peek into what my producer Les Les and I have been cooking up for my upcoming LP.  

New Wave Vocals cross with native Marimbas over tribal drums creating a sound ready for the dance floor.  It activates freedom of expression with a message to GO forward, casting aside distractions while giving your all in every area of life . “Go” has a vibe that is relentless like a mighty wind and the lyrics speak of our inner soul’s choices, overcoming the many voices that can pull us in different directions.  We say GO in order to move forward and not stand still, to find our answer beyond any chaos we encounter.

Music has saved my life, and I feel honored to share this song with you in acknowledgement of our culture of change and uplifting momentum. My hope is that this song inspires you to take action on that “one” thing that takes your life to the next level in 2023.

Graphics : Lee Robson Spence
Photography: Skyler Wagoner
